Package: altfuelr
Title: Provides an interface to the NREL Alternate Fuels Locator API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kitt",
           family = "Burch",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "christopher.m.burch@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6934-3325"))
Description: This package provides a number of functions to access the 
    National Energy Research Laboratory (NREL) Alternate Fuel Locator API. 
    The AFL shows the location of alternate fuel stations in the United States 
    and Canada. This package also includes the data from the NREL Alternate Fuel
    database as a data set.
